# Update Project Status

After significant work, update docs/project/status.md:

1. Update completion percentage for active milestones
2. Move completed items to "Accomplished" section  
3. Update "Last Updated" timestamp
4. Add any new blockers or dependencies
5. Suggest next priority tasks based on progress

Format:
```markdown
# Project: [Name]
**Last Updated:** [ISO Date]

## Current Milestone: [Name] (X% complete)
- [ ] Task 1
- [x] Completed task
- [ ] Task 3

## Accomplished This Session
- Specific achievement 1
- Specific achievement 2

## Next Priorities
1. Highest priority
2. Second priority

## Blockers
- None / [Specific blocker]